  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The research will examine psychotherapists' preferences for theoretical client
      characteristics, such as age, gender, personality characteristics and symptoms. The research
      will also examine the preferences' influence on the therapeutic alliance, from the
      therapist's and the client's point of view.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
